    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. can u be more specific though? like when u say \"well-tailored, conservative attire,\" can u give some actual examples of what that looks like? like if im at a high-stakes meeting in singapore or london or dubai, what is the actual uniform for someone who wants to be taken seriously as a top-tier executive?",
